    "body": "When you have integer indices it becomes ambiguous what your example really means.\nNegative indices works fine for non-int indices:\n\nIn [19]: s = Series(np.random.randn(3), ['a','b','c'])\n\nIn [20]: s\nOut[20]: \na    0.264423\nb    2.492051\nc    0.427773\n\nIn [21]: s[-1]\nOut[21]: 0.42777314897278684\n"
